posts.post_title: Hindu SL'ers ALL SOLD OR TRADED
posts.post_content:
Posted By: Rick McQuillan
Hello, I have 1 Hindu SL'er left to sell or trade.  Here is the deal with the trades.  I would like to trade this Hindu for low grade T206's or T205's.  I am looking mostly for commons, although I would trade for HOF'ers or SL'ers.  I prefer raw, but I will take graded.  I am looking for cards that would grade 1.5 to 2.5, with little or no writing or paper loss,and untrimmed.  At the bottom of this page I have listed the T206's and T205's that I have.

If you would rather purchase the cards, the Otey is TRADED, the Coles is SOLD, and the Guiheen is $95.  Prices include shipping and insurance.

PayPal is preferred - I don't charge any extra fees.  Checks and money orders are also OK.  Send emails to:  rickmcquillan@gmail.com

Thanks,
Rick
